description: There are a lot of empty shelves and signs that say ‘temporarily out of stock’ in Europe. The pendulum swings from east to west and it is a sign for what is coming to the U.S. When we rely on supermarkets for food, we will always be limited to what they are able to ship into the store. As times become more uncertain it is very important for us to learn how to grow our own food so that we do not have to depend on others.
